  "title": "The three levels of ecosystem thinking and when to apply them",
  "description": "A three-column infographic showing three thinking levels (L1 Portfolio, L2 Market, L3 Platform) with left-side visual diagrams (concentric rings and a zoomed platform diagram), central explanatory text for each level, and right-side guidance on when to apply each level including example companies.",
  "language": "en",
  "image_dimensions": {
