        "sector labels near ring: Transport, Trip Planning, Stay, Maintenance",
        "several node markers on ring and center user icon",
        "directional arrows around ring indicating flow"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "visual_zoom_box",
      "type": "diagram",
      "diagram_type": "zoomed_platform",
      "represents": "L3 Platform Level (Individual Business)",
      "position": { "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.02, "y": 0.60, "w": 0.36, "h": 0.34 } },
      "colors": { "platform_center": "dark_teal_text", "partner_icons": ["teal","orange","green","pink"] },
      "annotations": [
        "boxed zoom showing central 'Platform' circle with surrounding colored user/partner icons",
        "illustrates consumers, producers, partners around a platform core"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "thinking_heading",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Thinking Level",
      "role": "section_heading",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.41, "y": 0.12, "w": 0.22, "h": 0.06 },
      "style": { "font_weight": "bold", "color": "dark_teal_text" }
    },
    {
      "id": "L1_heading",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "L1 - Portfolio Level (Multi-Market)",
      "role": "subheading",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.41, "y": 0.18, "w": 0.33, "h": 0.06 },
      "style": { "font_weight": "bold", "color": "dark_teal_text" }
    },
    {
      "id": "L1_body",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Especially bigger corporates have build over time a big portfolio of different businesses - organized by business units - covering multiple different markets. Each segment represents a specific market ecosystem -> this perspective helps you to align company wide portfolios.",
      "role": "description",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.41, "y": 0.24, "w": 0.33, "h": 0.12 },
      "style": { "font_size": "small", "color": "dark_teal_text" }
    },
    {
      "id": "L2_heading",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "L2 - (Single) Market Level",
      "role": "subheading",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.41, "y": 0.38, "w": 0.33, "h": 0.06 },
      "style": { "font_weight": "bold", "color": "dark_teal_text" }
    },
    {
      "id": "L2_body",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "The market level perspective dives deeper into the understanding of a selected market. It helps to identify key players in the market as well as critical control points and new growth opportunities in this area.",
      "role": "description",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.41, "y": 0.44, "w": 0.33, "h": 0.12 },
      "style": { "font_size": "small", "color": "dark_teal_text" }
    },
    {
      "id": "L3_heading",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "L3 - Platform Level (Individual Business)",
      "role": "subheading",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.41, "y": 0.60, "w": 0.33, "h": 0.06 },
      "style": { "font_weight": "bold", "color": "dark_teal_text" }
    },
    {
      "id": "L3_body",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "This level helps you to understand the key users (consumers, producers, partners) of your platform business. This is very specific business/venture oriented and helps dedicated startup teams to make decisions and to unlock network effects.",
      "role": "description",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.41, "y": 0.66, "w": 0.33, "h": 0.12 },
      "style": { "font_size": "small", "color": "dark_teal_text" }
    },
    {
      "id": "when_heading",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "When to apply?",
      "role": "section_heading",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.76, "y": 0.12, "w": 0.22, "h": 0.06 },
      "style": { "font_weight": "bold", "color": "dark_teal_text" }
    },
    {
      "id": "L1_when",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "You are a big corporate / super platform and you want a holistic strategy for your business model portfolio (e.g. BASF, Bosch, Apple, Insurance companies, ...)",
      "role": "guidance",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.70, "y": 0.18, "w": 0.28, "h": 0.14 },
      "style": { "font_size": "small", "color": "dark_teal_text", "font_style": "italic" }
    },
    {
      "id": "L2_when",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "You want to understand and explore a specific market ecosystem with its players, control points and growth opportunities. (relevant for Startups and Corporates to create a market understanding)",
      "role": "guidance",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.70, "y": 0.36, "w": 0.28, "h": 0.14 },
      "style": { "font_size": "small", "color": "dark_teal_text", "font_style": "italic" }
    },
    {
      "id": "L3_when",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "You plan to build and scale a platform business and you want to understand the ecosystem of users (relevant for platform ventures)",
      "role": "guidance",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.70, "y": 0.60, "w": 0.28, "h": 0.12 },
      "style": { "font_size": "small", "color": "dark_teal_text", "font_style": "italic" }
    },
    {
      "id": "example_companies",
      "type": "list",
      "items": ["BASF", "Bosch", "Apple", "Insurance companies"],
      "role": "examples",
      "bbox_norm": { "x": 0.70, "y": 0.24, "w": 0.28, "h": 0.06 }
    }
  ],
  "notes": "All bounding boxes (bbox_norm) are approximate normalized positions (x,y,w,h) relative to the image size."
}

